    "description": "<p>We are looking to hire an iOS Developer (f/m/d) to join our app development team at DoctorBox. DoctorBox is one of the leading European digital health platforms for patients.</p>\n<p><strong>Tasks</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Develop, improve and maintain the DoctorBox native iOS application and further app projects</li>\n<li>Contribute to our UX and design concepts</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Swift (very good knowledge, if possible also experience with RxSwift)</li>\n<li>JavaScript knowledge: node js, electron js, possibly also react native.</li>\n<li>Objective-C</li>\n<li>Basic knowledge of C is an advantage (OpenSSL)</li>\n<li>Software Architecture and Design Patterns</li>\n<li>Experience with REST APIs and REST clients (Insomnia, Postman)</li>\n<li>Realm database</li>\n<li>Basic knowledge of cryptography</li>\n<li>Basic knowledge of Android programming, Java</li>\n<li>German is an advantage, the app is offered in English and German</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Shape the future of German healthcare</li>\n<li>Working with our team on location in Berlin, Germany with remote office days, complete remote work can be discussed</li>\n<li>We encourage learning for personal and professional growth</li>\n<li>Flexible working hours</li>\n<li>Long-term employment without time limitation</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You are welcome to submit your application online in German or English. For questions, please don’t hesitate to contact us. We look forward to receiving your complete application, including CV, a cover letter and relevant references with the following information: Job title, salary expectations and earliest start date via the 'Apply' button or to: DoctorBox GmbH - HR - Knesebeckstraße 69-61 - 10719 Berlin Germany.</p>\n",
