    "company_url": "http://www.lorienglobal.com",
    "location": "Soho, London",
    "title": "Backend Developer - Rightmove.co.uk",
    "description": "<p>As one of the most established digital businesses in the UK, and a household name, Rightmove has an exciting tech offering. Our tech stack is built on modern design principles with a Java/Spring Boot backend, a React web frontend (moving towards a Node.js front architecture) and mainly Swift/Kotlin in our native apps.  We make extensive use of Elasticsearch for our core search services and application logging/metrics, and Kafka for asynchronous messaging and streaming.</p>\n<p>Our applications are also built to a microservices architecture pattern, and we use Docker for all recent applications.</p>\n<p>And, did you know?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Our website and apps receive over 140m visits a month – more than ASOS, Instagram and Wikipedia – making us one of the UK’s top visited sites</li>\n<li>We manage 70TB of data, housed over 15,000 servers</li>\n<li>We did nearly 1,500 code releases last year!</li>\n</ul>\n<p>At Rightmove, we’re passionate about teams being involved from the beginning. We have cross-functional teams owning parts of the Rightmove experience, made up of design, product and engineering, as well as a set of specialists and teams focused on infrastructure, support and tooling. Together, we work on everything from product discovery to systems design, user interactions and delivering, with continued support and product evolution.</p>\n<p>We have a keen engineering community with a strong interest in keeping their skills up to date and in benefiting from new technology and approaches. As a result, there are fantastic opportunities to develop your tech career, learn new skills and try out the latest technologies, while building on Rightmove’s already highly successful, large scale platform with real autonomy.</p>\n<p>Does this sound like somewhere you could excel?</p>\n<p>Then apply now and Rightmove’s technology recruitment partner Lorien will be in touch about next steps!</p>\n<p>Apply here: <a href=\"https://www.lorienglobal.com/en/jobs?keywords=Rightmove.co.uk%20-%20Developer%20%E2%80%93%20Java%2FSpring%20Boot%2FMicroservices&amp;utm_source=RIGHTMOVE-NEW&amp;utm_medium=JAVADEVELOPER&amp;utm_campaign=GITHUB2\">https://www.lorienglobal.com/en/jobs?keywords=Rightmove.co.uk%20-%20Developer%20%E2%80%93%20Java%2FSpring%20Boot%2FMicroservices&amp;utm_source=RIGHTMOVE-NEW&amp;utm_medium=JAVADEVELOPER&amp;utm_campaign=GITHUB2</a></p>\n<p>Tech Stack: Java, Spring Boot, Node, React, Elasticsearch, Microservices architecture</p>\n",
    "how_to_apply": "<p>Email your resume to Eliza-Grace Eaton at <a href=\"mailto:Eliza-Grace.Eaton@lorienglobal.com\">Eliza-Grace.Eaton@lorienglobal.com</a> or apply here: <a href=\"https://www.lorienglobal.com/en/jobs?keywords=Rightmove.co.uk%20-%20Developer%20%E2%80%93%20Java%2FSpring%20Boot%2FMicroservices&amp;utm_source=RIGHTMOVE-NEW&amp;utm_medium=JAVADEVELOPER&amp;utm_campaign=GITHUB2\">https://www.lorienglobal.com/en/jobs?keywords=Rightmove.co.uk%20-%20Developer%20%E2%80%93%20Java%2FSpring%20Boot%2FMicroservices&amp;utm_source=RIGHTMOVE-NEW&amp;utm_medium=JAVADEVELOPER&amp;utm_campaign=GITHUB2</a></p>\n",
